sinesses he began his career as an auditor with deloitte and touche llp where he specialized in the audits of financial services companies tom also served as assistant director of princeton university’s investment administration team tom holds a bs in accounting and an mba in finance from rider university tom remains a loyal supporter of rider where he is an adjunct professor of accounting at rider and sits on the university’s accounting advisory council tom was recently the president of the flemingtonraritan lions club and is an adventurer who enjoys active outdoor sports such as surfing and snowboarding he is a teacher at heart and loves to share his knowledge with others he is devoted to his wife michele and five daughters and places a high value on giving back to the community through service and charitable work steven m fox cofounder chief operating officer steven is the chief operating officer coo and founding partner at alliance wealth management group he has almost 0 years of professional experience in the financial services industry steven has extensive experience with executing corporate strategy organizational leadership marketing and communications product strategy positioning public relations advertising and client experience steven graduated from tiffin university ohio with a bachelor of business administration bba degree he earned his master of business administration mba degree with a concentration in finance from grand canyon university in phoenix arizona steve currently serves as an advisory board member for the freedom valley ymca previously steven worked as a principal consultant at dbj interactive solutions senior manager at the vanguard group and most recently as an executive director at a private regional financial firm throughout his career steven has worked in a variety of challenging and rewarding positions that have allowed him to drive strategy manage operations lead initiatives develop new products create business plans and conduct resea